{
  "summary": "The extraction was partially successful but failed to achieve high accuracy due to line item mismatches and formatting discrepancies. While the total count of line items matched, the content did not: the model extracted an item ('Patron Silver') that was not in the gold list and missed one of the 'Chicken Caprese' entries present in the gold list. Additionally, there were minor formatting differences in the date, address, and subtotal.",
